    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crazy Pipes 3D</strong> is a fast-paced 3D puzzle game where you must connect pipes on a dynamic grid before water bursts out and chaos erupts! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your pipe system from the entry points to  exit points while avoiding obstacles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386960/extras/2025-06-11_21-18-58_screenshot.png?t=1755020807\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to replace pipes after a dynamite explosion, and build the longest, twistiest path to boost your score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386960/extras/2025-06-11_21-01-00_screenshot.png?t=1755020807\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle handcrafted puzzles in <strong>Normal Mode</strong>, where difficulty ramps up steadily to keep your brain on its toes. Or kick back in <strong>Endless Mode</strong>, a chill, timer-free experience with procedurally generated puzzles — perfect for relaxed pipe-building fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to outsmart the flood?</p>",
